        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/venezuela-refugee-crisis-8-million-migrants-2014-unhcr-report.png" alt="According to the UN's refugee agency, almost 8Mn Venezuelans have left their homeland since the crisis began in 2014" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
